2006-03-07  Chris Dunlap  <cdunlap@llnl.gov>

	* munge.spec: Fixed so the files in the munge-devel & munge-libs RPMs
	  are permissioned properly.

2006-02-28  Chris Dunlap  <cdunlap@llnl.gov>

	* : Released 0.5.1.

